rComments: Amazing prof. Exams are extremely hard!! The textbook helps but focus on the lecture slides carefully as her exams are based around them. Take time to understand the material do NOT just memorize - her exams are a lot of applications of the concepts in class. Spend a lot of time on this class or you will not do well.

She's supper easy when it comes to testing. No surprises on her midterms (there are 3, and no exams), and she lets you visit her labs. You should definitely do that because she puts 4 bonus points of her exam that you'd only be able to figure out if you went!

super nice prof but sometimes doesn't seem to know how to answer questions outside her provided slides. but all in all, an easy A as long as you attend class, add notes to her powerpoint and read the textbook.
